description: For sale: $325,000. Charming home nestled on a quiet lakeshore lot in a beautiful outdoor setting in Stacy. The lakefront view is paired with access to fishing, canoeing, and kayaking in Sherman Oaks Lake. Swans, ducks, geese and the occasional eagle make lake life enjoyable year round. The nearby Sunrise Prairie Trail offers more recreational opportunities like hiking, biking, and snowmobiling. Adding a home with vaulted ceilings, natural woodwork, and multiple decks with lake views really seals the deal. This turnkey property is a well maintained 3 level split that provides ample common areas, bedrooms and bathrooms. Second kitchen on main level makes for a great in law suite. Spray foam insulation in the garage makes a perfect workshop area. Easy access to I 35 makes a great commute to the cities.
